assistant: 1. Identify objects on the table.
2. Move to the table.
3. Pick up the wine glass from the table.
4. Place the wine glass in the cabinet.
5. Pick up the plate from the table.
6. Place the plate in the cabinet.
7. Pick up the packet of crackers from the table.
8. Place the packet of crackers in the cabinet.
9. Move to the counter.
10. Inspect objects on the counter.
11. Pick up the pitcher from the counter.
12. Remove the bottle from the pitcher.
13. Place the bottle in the cabinet.
14. Place the pitcher in the cabinet.
15. Move to the stove.
16. Inspect objects on the stove.
17. Pick up the pot from the stove.
18. Move to the sink.
19. Clean the pot.
20. Place the pot in the cabinet.
21. Inspect the floor for any misplaced items.
22. Verify that all objects are in their designated storage locations.
